Articles.Content:
Hello guys,

I am yinotaurus, I like orbial mechanics, obviously. I am a coder by trade and kin. That's about it.

I would like to ask you guys, I migrated my saves from windows to ubuntu, steam install 12 common mods (kas, mechjeb2, some save-file agnostic mods, ~12 total). Full career, level 3 tracking station. After I cp'd the file I am getting no more new asteroid around Kerbin for almos a year. I have time-warped 2 years and I am having no more asteroids.

Is this normal?

PS: I have active all 12 contract on my level 2 mission control.

Hello yin, and welcome to our forum.

Since your question is not a typical newbie greeting, it has been moved to the Support subforum so the right people will see it. Good luck with your problem.
